## Cancer-specific nuance
- “Cancer” alone is **not** a reason to default to LMWH for **AF stroke prevention**; DOACs are routinely used unless there are competing issues (drug–drug interactions with systemic therapy, GI lesions/bleeding risk, thrombocytopenia, absorption concerns). [1]

